OL,3,CAnti-Black discrimination 'baked' into
OL,4,CMet Police, review warns
OL,6,FDiscrimination has been "baked" into
OL,7,Fthe HR systems of the Metropolitan
OL,8,FPolice, a review of anti-Black racism
OL,9,Fwithin the force has warned.
OL,11,FThe independent report from Dr Shereen
OL,12,FDaniels, commissioned by the
OL,13,FMetropolitan Police Service, said
OL,14,Fdarker skinned staff are "labelled
OL,15,Fconfrontational" while lighter skinned
OL,16,Fstaff may receive quicker empathy and
OL,17,Fleniency.
