OL,3,CAnti-Black discrimination 'baked' into
OL,4,CMet Police, review warns
OL,6,FThe internal review drew on more than
OL,7,F40 years of evidence and concluded
OL,8,Fthat the Met's systems, leadership,
OL,9,Fgovernance and culture are producing
OL,10,Fracial harm.
OL,12,FScotland Yard said it welcomed the
OL,13,Freport in full and recognised the
OL,14,Fscale of the challenges set out.
OL,16,FDr Daniels said discrimination is
OL,17,F"baked" into the "institutional
OL,18,Fdesign" of the force.
