OL,3,CAnti-Black discrimination 'baked' into
OL,4,CMet Police, review warns
OL,6,F"Plans that ignore this will always
OL,7,Freturn to the same logic, manage
OL,8,Fperception, avoid power, thus
OL,9,Fcontinuing the cycle," she added.
OL,11,FThe latest examination of the force
OL,12,Fcomes after Louise Casey's 2023
OL,13,Freview, commissioned after the murder
OL,14,Fof Sarah Everard, found the Met to be
OL,15,F"institutionally racist, misogynistic
OL,16,Fand homophobic".
