OL,3,CAnti-Black discrimination 'baked' into
OL,4,CMet Police, review warns
OL,6,FPrevious internal reviews have also
OL,7,Fcriticised the Met for being
OL,8,Fdiscriminatory, including the
OL,9,FMacPherson report in 1999 that called
OL,10,Fit "institutionally racist" after
OL,11,Fofficers mishandled the Stephen
OL,12,FLawrence case.
OL,14,FLawrence's mother welcomed the new
OL,15,Freport, but said it contained "nothing
OL,16,Fthat I did not already know".
OL,18,FBaroness Doreen Lawrence's 18-year-old
OL,19,Fson was killed in a racist attack in
OL,20,Fsouth-east London in 1993.
