OL,3,CAnti-Black discrimination 'baked' into
OL,4,CMet Police, review warns
OL,6,FDr Daniels said: "For the Met, the
OL,7,Fchallenge ahead is to build the
OL,8,Fleadership discipline to face what the
OL,9,Freport has revealed and act on its
OL,10,Ffindings in a way that protects the
OL,11,Fpublic rather than the institution."
OL,13,FCommissioner Sir Mark Rowley called Dr
OL,14,FDaniels' report "powerful" and stated:
OL,15,F"It calls out that further systemic,
OL,16,Fstructural, cultural change is needed.
OL,17,FI asked for a review focused on the
OL,18,FMet and Black communities which
OL,19,Fchallenges us to go further in
OL,20,Fbecoming an actively anti-racist
OL,21,Forganisation.
